Track Who Ends Enhanced Messaging Sessions

A new field on enhanced messaging sessions shows whether a session was ended by the customer, the agent, a bot, or automation. Add the Ended By Type (EndedByType) field to your custom report types to get insight into enhanced messaging activity.

Where: This change applies to enhanced Messaging channels and Messaging for In-App and Web. View required editions.

How: The Ended By Type field has four possible values: End User, Agent, Bot, and System. “End User” refers to the customer. “System” can mean three things.

After being inactive for the maximum amount of time, the status automatically updated to Ended.
The status automatically updated to Ended due to any automation in place.
Something went wrong and the session ended with a status of Error.
